Nkera e Nkai


1   Eng'ura eneba enyorrata natonyorra iyiook Papa, pee eipoti iyiook aajo nkera e Nkai; naa kesipa eikira. Ore pee meyiolo iyiook enkop enkaraki neitu eiyiolou ninye. 
2  Ilanyor laainei, kira taata iyiook inkera Enkai neton eitu elioyu enikiyooki aatiu, kake kiyiolo aajo ore pee elioyu ninye nikitiu anaa ninye amu aikidol ninye eneikununo.


3  Naa ore pooki ng'ae oata ilo siligi te ninye neitisiny kewan anaa enasinya ninye. 
4  Ore pooki ng'ae oas intorrok neeta entiyoto e mpaashata oo nkitanapat; ing'ok empaashata o nkitanapat. 
5   Iyiololo aajo eewuo ninye pee etum aawa ng'ok, nemetii ng'ok atua ninye. 
6  Meetae oloton ti atua ninye oas ng'ok, nemeetae oloas ng'ok etoduaa ninye aashu otayiolo ninye. 
7  Na kera kutiti, emincho elej intae oltung'ani. Ore ilo oas esidai naa olasipani, anaa paa asipani ninye. 
8  Ore ilo oas ing'ok naa ole sheitani, amu etaasa apa sheitani ing'ok ebaiki enkiterunoto. Ina pee etaliee Oinoti le Nkai pee eidaikie isiaaitin e Sheitani. 
9  Meetae oloino te Nkai oas ing'ok amu eton empukunoto e Nkai tiatua ninye. Nemeas ninye ing'ok amu keino te Nkai. 
10  Tena eidimi aatodol nchere kaku nkera e Nkai, naa kakua nkera e Sheitani: ore pooki ng'ae lemeas enaishaakino neme ole Nkai, naa neijia etiu ilo lemenyor olalashe lenye.

Tonyorra olikae olikae


11   Amu ele kilikuai itoning'o apake te nkiterunoto, nchere matonyorrata olikae o likae, 
12   pee mikitiu anaa Kain le ilo torrono otara apa ninye olalashe lenye metua. Naa ainyoo pee etara ninye metua? Enkaraki naa torrok nkiasin enye naasidain ino lalashe lenye. 
13  Eming'asia lalashera, nchere eiba intae enkop. 
14   Eikiyiolo iyiook aajo kitupukutuo te keeya aajing empuaan, amu kinyor ilalashera. Ore olemenyorrisho etii atua keeya. 
15  Ore pooki ng'ae oiba olalashe lenye naa olarani, niyiololo intae aajo meetae olarani omany enkishui nemeish atua ninye. 
16  Ena kiyiolounye enyorrata, nchere eirragie ninye enkishui enye te nkaraki iyiook; neishiakino sii ninche iyiook te nikirragie enkishui ang te nkaraki lalashera.


17  Kake te neeta ake oltung'ani masaa e nkop neduaaki olalashe enyamali, neitoki ake aiken oltau ti alo ninye, kaji naa etamanya enyorrata e Nkai ti atua ninye? 
18  Na kera kutiti emikinyorrisho to rorei ake aashu to lng'ejep kake te asata o te sipata.

Enkitieunoto te dukuya e Nkai


19  Ena kiyiolounye aajo kira iyiook ile sipata, nikintadedeyie ltauja lang te dukuya ninye, 
20  enoshi kata naiguenare iyiook iltauja lang, amu kitok Enkai alang iltauja lang, neyiolo pooki toki. 
21  Ilanyor laainei, te nemeiguenare iyook iltauja lang, nikiata enkitieunoto nikintoriokinore Enkai; 
22  naa eikitum pooki toki nikiomonu, amu eikimbung nkitanapat enyena nikias ina naitiship ninye. 
23   Naa ena enkitanapata enye, nchere mairuko enkarna o Inoti lenye Yesu Kristo nikinyorruno maate, anaa ina ake naitanapa iyiook. 
24  Ore lelo pooki ooibung nkitanapat enyena netoni ninche tiatua ninye. Naa ena kiyiolounye nchere etonita ninye ti atua iyiook, te nkaraki ina Kiyang'et Sinyati naishoo ninye iyiook.

